{"tid":1296522,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港的火星，會在中國引發燎原大火","createTime":"2019-07-08T11:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T12:02:53.000Z","uid":270374,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"47048112f889e5d59d02c6aa7ca666c11d3f18f3","tid":1296522,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:44:12.000Z","msg":"中央社報道，據了解，十餘名曾在私人微信群組討論並表示支持香港反《逃犯條例》修訂示威者的北京民眾，近日陸續受到警方約談盤問。報道指，主要話題發起者先是遭到警方約談，近日更遭國保二度警告，指先前的行為已是「尋釁滋事」，倘若再轉發相關言論，就涉及「煽動顛覆政權」。<br />\n<br />\n中央社在發自北京的報道指，對於這次中國官方對香港事件的宣傳與定調手法，一名曾經歷「六四」事件的北京體制內分析人士近日表示，中共高層最擔心的，其實是「香港的火星，會在中國引發燎原大火」。<br />\n<br />\n原文﹕眾新聞<br />\n微信群組支持「反送中」港示威者 北京十餘人遭盤問 被指「尋釁滋事」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/21917/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E9%83%A8-21917/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E7%BE%A4%E7%B5%84%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E3%80%8C%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E3%80%8D%E6%B8%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E5%8D%81%E9%A4%98%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%AD%E7%9B%A4%E5%95%8F-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E3%80%8C%E5%B0%8B%E9%87%81%E6%BB%8B%E4%BA%8B%E3%80%8D?fbclid=IwAR1OBL_QD7EjpTE_I8u0RsuzJ40VSqxpkTO3VnTA0MGrqYI-gvKEZRvXPv0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F21917%2F%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E4%25BF%25A1-%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%2589%25E9%2583%25A8-21917%2F%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E7%25B5%2584%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E3%2580%258D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585-%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%258D%2581%25E9%25A4%2598%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%259B%25A4%25E5%2595%258F-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25B0%258B%25E9%2587%2581%25E6%25BB%258B%25E4%25BA%258B%25E3%2580%258D%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1OBL_QD7EjpTE_I8u0RsuzJ40VSqxpkTO3VnTA0MGrqYI-gvKEZRvXPv0&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpSwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=4f